candidates.title: Add dependency `registry` to `cargo metadata`.
candidates.body:
This adds the `registry` field for dependencies for alternate registries in
`cargo metadata`.

candidates.title: Allow testsuite warnings in dev
candidates.body:
This makes the deny(warnings) in the testsuite conditional on a new
"deny-warnings" feature, that is then enabled in CI.

Ideally I could use the (reasonably well established) CI env var (like
we do for proptests), but I don't know how to get the attribute to be
defined in terms of an env var.

candidates.title: Display errors when `cargo fix` fails.
candidates.body: It can be difficult to figure out what's wrong when a user reports that `cargo fix` fails. It can be hard to figure out which suggestion caused a compile error, especially if the error is in another file/location.

candidates.title: Migrate to some Rust 2018 idioms
candidates.body: Run a few lints, hand-edit a few things, otherwise try to help push Cargo into the 2018 edition!
